Global Automotive Lock Market Insights
Automotive Lock Market size was valued at USD 25.4 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 35.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Automotive Lock Market Overview
The global automotive lock market was valued at approximately USD 10.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 15.3 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.2%. The increasing demand for advanced security features in vehicles, the shift towards electric vehicles (EVs), and rising concerns about vehicle safety are the major factors propelling the market growth. Additionally, the integration of smart locking systems and keyless entry technologies has further amplified the market dynamics. Automotive locks are essential components in vehicle security systems, and the demand is expected to continue rising as the automotive industry increasingly prioritizes safety and convenience.

